flowRoot.flowPara: The backoffice has a administrative web gui and manual routines to interact with the system.
The repairteam moves the bikes to load stations and repair them when needed.
The customers can rent a bike using a ap and can control their account using a web gui.
The bikes communicates their position and status with the system and current stat us.
When a customer rents a bike, the bike communicates its position and speed and listens on commands from the system.
